@host = http://localhost:5096

### Create upload
POST {{host}}/uploads
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fileName": "sample.mp4",
  "contentType": "video/mp4"
}

### Start transcode
POST {{host}}/transcodes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "videoId": "REPLACE_WITH_VIDEO_ID"
}

### Poll status
GET {{host}}/transcodes/REPLACE_WITH_VIDEO_ID

### Fetch result
GET {{host}}/transcodes/REPLACE_WITH_VIDEO_ID/result
